name: A "Quiet" Night
description:
A "Quiet" Night

In this piece I've been exploring the circle generated by a field of single pixels and decided to shape them into what ended up with the piece. The oxymoron of having a quiet night that might be as explosive and full of color could not quite be like this.

You can find more on Twitter @generatecoll or Instagram @generate.collective (2021)

Size: 1000x1000 px
